data.title: Games Lists – Arcade Nostalgia
data.text:
Finally, after a long delay, I made the Pandora 10 game list it is no longer up to date 🙂 I just got the new Pandore Box V2 with 10888 games.

From now I will only install Arcade Machines Pandora Box 10 with 10888 games.

If you want to check out all the games from Pandora 10, please check the link bellow (the newest Pandora has ”only” 888 more games 🙂

Best Regards

Team Arcade Nostalgia
